%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Azam%20Khan%2C%20His%20Wife%20and%20Son%20Given%207-Year%20Jail%20Term%20in%20Fake%20Birth%20Certificate%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18180729%2Fimage-1402.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20local%20court%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2018)%20convicted%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20his%20wife%20Tazeen%20Fatima%2C%20and%20son%20Abdullah%20Azam%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20forgery%20of%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20birth%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20awarded%20them%20the%20maximum%20punishment%2C%20a%20seven-year%20jail%20term%2C%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Fazam-khan-wife-son-abdullah-7-year-jail-fake-birth-certificate-case-8988994%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20past%20one%20month%2C%20this%20is%20the%20fourth%20case%20in%20which%20Azam%20Khan%20has%20been%20convicted.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20second%20conviction%20of%20former%20MLA%20Abdullah%20Azam%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArun%20Parkash%20Saxena%2C%20a%20former%20district%20government%20counsel%2C%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20prosecution%2C%20told%20PTI%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20court%20verdict%2C%20the%20trio%20was%20taken%20into%20judicial%20custody%20and%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20jail%20from%20the%20court%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20register%20(FIR)%20in%20the%20case%20was%20lodged%20by%20a%20resident%2C%20Akash%20Saxena%20(who%20is%20now%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MLA)%2C%20at%20the%20Ganj%20police%20station%20in%20Rampur%2C%20on%20January%203%2C%202019.%20He%20had%20alleged%20that%20Khan%20and%20his%20wife%20helped%20their%20son%20obtain%20two%20fake%20date%20of%20birth%20certificates%20%E2%80%93%20one%20from%20Lucknow%20and%20another%20from%20Rampur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20charge-sheet%2C%20in%20the%20certificate%20issued%20by%20the%20Rampur%20municipality%2C%20Abdullah%20Azam%E2%80%99s%20date%20of%20birth%20was%20mentioned%20as%20January%201%2C%201993.%20The%20other%20certificate%20said%20he%20was%20born%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20September%2030%2C%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20is%20accused%20of%20using%20the%20first%20one%20for%20his%20passport%20and%20for%20travels%20abroad%2C%20while%20the%20second%20one%20was%20used%20for%20government%20records%20and%20for%20getting%20affiliation%20with%20Jauhar%20University%2C%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20convicted%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20420%20(cheating%20and%20dishonestly%20inducing%20delivery%20of%20property)%2C%20467%20(forgery%20of%20valuable%20security%2C%20will%2C%20etc.)%2C%20468%20(forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20cheating)%2C%20471%20(using%20as%20genuine%20a%20forged%201%5Bdocument%20or%20electronic%20record%5D)%20and%20120-B%20(criminal%20conspiracy).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2026%2C%202020%2C%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20son%20had%20surrendered%20before%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Rampur%2C%20over%20their%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20Later%2C%20all%20three%20obtained%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20assumed%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202017%2C%20Azam%20Khan%20has%20faced%2081%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20Rampur%20on%20multiple%20charges%2C%20such%20as%20land-grabbing%2C%20cheating%2C%20and%20criminal%20trespass.%20Additionally%2C%20Azam%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Tanzeen%20Fatima%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Abdullah%20Azam%2C%20have%20been%20implicated%20in%20some%20of%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20a%20Rampur%20court%20sentenced%20Azam%20Khan%20to%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht