ttps%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Ffocus%2Fbeanie-feldstein-on-being-jewish-1235759363%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Ffocus%2Fbeanie-feldstein-on-being-jewish-1235759363%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Ffocus%2Fbeanie-feldstein-on-being-jewish-1235759363%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20mysterious%204%2C000-year-old%20slab%20may%20be%20a%20treasure%20map%20that%20could%20point%20the%20way%20to%20long-lost%20Bronze%20Age%20riches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20shows%20the%20engravings%20on%20the%20slab%20dots%20and%20cups%20carved%20in%20the%20rock%20are%20tied%20together%20by%20lines.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652fc1efbe9edfa8eda37c8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Saint-B%C3%A9lec%20slab%20was%20long%20a%20mysterious%20set%20of%20engravings%2C%20but%20scientists%20now%20think%20it's%20a%20map%20that%20could%20point%20to%20long-lost%20archaeological%20sites.%3Cp%3ED.%20Gliksman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20mysterious%20millennia-old%20slab%20sat%20undisturbed%20in%20storage%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScientists%20found%20it%20was%20a%20gigantic%20map%2C%20likely%20used%20by%20a%20Bronze%20Age%20prince%20to%20rule%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20now%20want%20to%20use%20this%20%26quot%3Btreasure%20map%26quot%3B%20to%20uncover%20lost%20archaeological%20sites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMysterious%20engravings%20on%20an%20ancient%20stone%20slab%2C%20long%20relegated%20to%20the%20storage%20area%20of%20an%20ancient%20castle%2C%20might%20reveal%20the%20locations%20of%20long-lost%20Bronze%20Age%20treasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20analysis%20of%20the%20slab%2C%20which%20had%20been%20forgotten%20since%20it%20was%20first%20discovered%20in%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20suggests%20it%20could%20mark%20the%20location%20of%20forgotten%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbronze-age-cauldrons-show-evidence-what-ancient-feasts-looked-like-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBronze%20Age%3C%2Fa%3E%20sites%20dating%20back%20to%20between%202%2C150%20and%201%2C600%20BC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20the%20map%20to%20try%20to%20find%20archaeological%20sites%20is%20a%20great%20approach.%20We%20never%20work%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yvan%20Pailler%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Western%20Brittany%2C%20told%20Agence%20France%20Presse%20(AFP)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencealert.com%2Fstrangely-engraved-rock-is-giant-treasure-map-archaeologists-say%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScience%20Alert%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20treasure%20map%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESecrets%20from%20the%20Bronze%20Age%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20du%20Ch%C3%A2tellier%2C%20an%20archaeologist%20of%20the%20late%201800s%2C%20was%20clearly%20struck%20by%20the%20profound%20significance%20of%20the%20gigantic%20block%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Saint-B%C3%A9lec%20slab%2C%20when%20he%20first%20uncovered%20it%20lining%20an%20ancient%20burial%20mound%20in%20Brittany%2C%20on%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20France%20in%201900.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20marveled%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bremarkable%20monument's%26quot%3B%20delicate%20engravings%20of%20cups%2C%20circles%2C%20and%20lines%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20quite%20know%20what%20to%20make%20of%20it%2C%20per%20a%20post%20written%20about%20the%20finding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fla-redecouverte-de-la-dalle-de-saint-belec-169413%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%202021%20in%20The%20Conversation.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20he%20would%20go%20to%20his%20grave%20without%20uncovering%20the%20secrets%20of%20the%20mysterious%20rock.%20The%20slab%20remained%20du%20Ch%C3%A2tellier's%20castle%20storage%20and%20was%20passed%20on%20to%20the%20French%20Museum%20of%20National%20Archaeology%20after%20his%20death%20in%201911.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20only%20a%20century%20later%20that%20the%20hidden%20meaning%20behind%20the%20prehistoric%20engravings%20may%20have%20been%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20engraved%20slab%20is%20shown%20placed%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20a%20scientist%20leans%20over%20it%20holding%20a%20camera.%20The%20slab%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20scientist.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652fd060be9edfa8eda3828f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20slab%20is%20shown%20here%20being%20photographed%20by%20a%20scientist%3Cp%3EY.%20Pailler%2C%20Inrap%2C%20Examining%20the%20Saint-B%C3%A9lec%20slab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20archeological%20treasure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20sleuthing%20to%20recover%20the%20lost%20slab%2C%20whose%20pictures%20had%20been%20shared%20in%20archaeological%20circles%20since%20the%201900s%2C%20experts%20conducted%20a%20thorough%20analysis%20of%20the%20engravings%2C%20including%20scanning%20the%20rock%20in%20a%203D%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20now%20have%20the%20technology%20to%20know%20exactly%20what%20an%20area%20looks%20like%20from%20above%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20lines%20and%20bumps%20in%20the%20rock%20became%20immediately%20apparent%2C%20said%20Pailler%2C%20who%20led%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20slab%2C%20per%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scientists%20found%20an%2080%25%20match%20with%20the%20rivers%20and%20mountains%20of%20the%20Roudouallec%20area%20in%20Brittany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%2C%20published%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhal.science%2Fhal-03507764%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBulletin%20de%20la%20Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9%20pr%C3%A9historique%20fran%C3%A7aise%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%202021%2C%20identified%20the%20map%20as%20the%20oldest%20cartographical%20representation%20of%20a%20territory%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scientists%20are%20now%20hoping%20to%20uncover%20the%20last%20secrets%20of%20the%20map%20to%20find%20new%20Bronze%20Age%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchaeologists-upper-class-bronze-age-man-who-underwent-brain-surgery-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchaeological%20sites.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20missing%20now%20is%20the%20map%20key%2C%20the%20decoder%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cl%C3%A9ment%20Nicolas%2C%20a%20lead%20researcher%20on%20the%20dig%20from%20Bournemouth%20University%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inrap.fr%2Fla-plus-ancienne-carte-d-europe-15574%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20post%20for%20research%20institute%20Inrap%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cups%2C%20they%20believe%2C%20could%20be%20burial%20mounds%2C%20houses%2C%20or%20even%20mineral%20deposits%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20researchers%20have%20been%20excavating%20the%20site%20where%20the%20slab%20was%20originally%20found%20to%20better%20date%20the%20discovery%2C%20Pailler%20said%20per%20AFP.%20The%20dig%20has%20uncovered%20some%20lost%20fragments%20of%20the%20slab%20that%20had%20been%20snapped%20off%20and%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20map%20was%20likely%20used%20by%20a%20despotic%20Bronze%20Age%20ruler%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20could%20point%20the%20way%20to%20a%20burial%20mound%20of%20a%20prince%2C%20per%20a%20post%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmusee-archeologienationale.fr%2Fcollection%2Fobjet%2Fdalle-gravee-de-saint-belec%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20National%20Archaeology%20Museum%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20likely%20that%20it%20was%20once%20used%20by%20a%20prince%20from%20the%20early%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-humans-took-hallucinogens-drugs-3000-years-ago-rituals-study-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBronze%20Age%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20would%20have%20directed%20a%20small%20military%20faction%20to%20forcibly%20rule%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20rulers%20were%20typically%20buried%20with%20bronze%20daggers%2C%20arrowheads%2C%20and%20sometimes%20golden%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20the%20map%20was%20carelessly%20broken%20into%20pieces%20to%20be%20used%20as%20building%20materials%20could%20be%20the%20sign%20that%20the%20prince's%20rule%20in%20that%20area%20had%20come%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20engraved%20slab%20no%20longer%20made%20sense%20and%20was%20doomed%20by%20being%20broken%20up%20and%20used%20as%20building%20material%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nicolas%2C%20per%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-000-year-engraved-rock-slab-treasure-map-bronze-age-archaeological-sites-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697632687000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652fc1efbe9edfa8eda37c8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-000-year-engraved-rock-slab-treasure-map-bronze-age-archaeological-sites-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mysterious%20engravings%20on%20an%20ancient%20stone%20slab%2C%20long%20relegated%20to%20the%20storage%20area%20of%20an%20ancient%20castle%2C%20might%20reveal%20the%20locations%20of%20long-lost%20Bronze%20Age%20treasure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mguenot%40businessinsider.com%20(Marianne%20Guenot)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-000-year-engraved-rock-slab-treasure-map-bronze-age-archaeological-sites-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%