Four-work%2Feducation%5C%22%3EAs%20of%20June%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%2017%2C091%20Ekal%20schools%2C%20where%20more%20than%205%2C16%2C562%20students%20were%20enrolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98War%20against%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Palia%20Kalan%2C%20Sanju%20Kumari%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20woman%20from%20the%20Tharu%20tribe%2C%20talks%20very%20fondly%20of%20%E2%80%9CHinduism%E2%80%9D.%20She%20has%20attended%20various%20women%E2%80%99s%20meet-ups%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20Lucknow.%20%E2%80%9COur%20people%20(Tharu%20tribe)%20have%20been%20away%20from%20Hinduism%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20now%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20we%20are%20realising%20the%20importance%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20the%20war%20that%20should%20be%20waged%20against%20the%20enemies%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumari%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20class%20of%2018%20women%20students%2C%20Kumari%20teaches%20them%20Hindu%20prayers%20and%20morals%2C%20how%20to%20stitch%20clothes%2C%20and%20who%20the%20%E2%80%9Cactual%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D%20are.%20For%20a%20year%20now%2C%20Kumari%20has%20been%20educating%20women%20up%20to%20the%20age%20of%2030%20about%20the%20dangers%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%20can%20pose.%20Kumari%20and%20Chandravati%20Rana%20%E2%80%93%20another%20Tharu%20woman%20who%20is%20also%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20teaching%20women%20about%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20an%20Islamophobic%20conspiracy%20suggesting%20that%20Muslim%20men%20lure%20Hindu%20women%20into%20marrying%20them%20only%20to%20convert%20them%20to%20Islam%20and%20to%20establish%20demographic%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2