0and%20filmed%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20widely%20shared%20post%20claimed%20to%20show%20footage%20of%20Hamas%20or%20Israel%20faking%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20child%20by%20the%20other%20side.%20The%20video%20was%20actually%20footage%20from%20a%20film%20posted%20to%20TikTok%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EStop%20trying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20gotten%20so%20bad%20that%20Marcus%20Hutchins%2C%20a%20famous%20cybersecurity%20hacker%2C%20is%20now%20advising%20news%20organizations%20and%20journalists%20like%20Sardarizadeh%20to%20just%20steer%20clear%20of%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20not%20try%20to%20correct%20erroneous%20information%20posted%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJournalists%20may%20think%20they're%20countering%20misinformation%20by%20debunking%20it%2C%20but%20often%20they%20don't%20fundamentally%20understand%20the%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40malwaretech%2Fpost%2FCyggpagRovs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20interact%20with%20a%20post%20(even%20to%20debunk%20it)%2C%20you%20boost%20it%20in%20the%20algorithm%2C%20causing%20the%20original%20to%20spread%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENews%20is%20'too%20risky'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20some%20people%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20news%20on%20Threads%2C%20the%20new%20Twitter-like%20platform%20from%20Meta.%20Hundreds%20of%20people%20piled%20into%20posts%20from%20Mosseri%20asking%20for%20tools%20on%20the%20platform%20that%20would%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20find%20high%20quality%20news.%20Mosseri%2C%20who%20now%20runs%20Threads%20and%20previously%20spent%20several%20years%20overseeing%20Facebook's%20News%20Feed%2C%20isn't%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20anti-news%2C%26quot%3B%20Mosseri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40mosseri%2Fpost%2FC