insider.com%2Ffacebook-news-ban-in-canada-causes-more-app-downloads-usage-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eactively%20blocked%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20due%20to%20pending%20legislation%20in%20the%20country%20that%20would%20require%20the%20company%20to%20pay%20for%20news%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EX%20is%20for%20'grifters'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20on%20X%2C%20the%20paid%20verification%20service%20Musk%20rolled%20out%20gives%20any%20paying%20user%20algorithmic%20amplification.%20There's%20also%20a%20new%20system%20of%20direct%20payment%20for%20those%20who%20gain%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20changes%2C%20combined%20with%20content%20moderation%20job%20cuts%2C%20have%20turned%20X%20into%20a%20platform%20where%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20grifters%20and%20professional%20(sometimes%20state-aligned)%20teams%26quot%3B%20run%20amok%2C%20according%20to%20Alex%20Stamos%20of%20Stanford's%20Internet%20Observatory%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20Meta's%20chief%20security%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20asked%20Meta%2C%20X%20and%20TikTok%20for%20specifics%20on%20how%20they%20were%20working%20to%20combat%20false%20and%20unverified%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20would%20not%20share%20details%20on%20any%20accounts%20or%20posts%20it%20has%20taken%20action%20on%2C%20but%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20actively%20monitoring%20content%20related%20to%20the%20conflict%20and%20removing%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%2C%20we%20quickly%20established%20a%20special%20operations%20center%20staffed%20with%20experts%2C%20including%20fluent%20Hebrew%20and%20Arabic%20speakers%2C%20to%20closely%20monitor%20and%20respond%20to%20this%20rapidly%20evolving%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20mobilized%20significant%20res