Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInteresting%20question%20to%20me%E2%80%A6the%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20huge%20story.%20This%20story%20would%20bring%20down%20any%20government.%20This%20is%20direct%20theft%20by%20a%20man%2C%20who%20has%20been%20protected%20again%2C%20and%20again%2C%20and%20again%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20And%20the%20surprising%20thing%20is%2C%20not%20a%20single%20Indian%20newspaper%20is%20interested%20in%20picking%20up%20the%20story%2C%20not%20a%20single%20media%20channel%20is%20interested%20in%20picking%20up%20the%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20giving%20electricity%20subsidies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20going%20to%20do%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20while%20we%20are%20giving%20electricity%20subsidies%2C%20Mr.%20Adani%20is%20over%20invoicing%20coal%20and%20stealing%20directly%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20comment%20on%20this.%20This%20cannot%20happen%20without%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20impossible.%20So%2C%20the%20question%20is%3A%20why%20is%20there%20no%20action%20being%20taken%20on%20this%20gentleman%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Will%20definitely%20get%20it%20done%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20January%2C%20US%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20alleged%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20and%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20regulatory%20mechanisms%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStock%20market%20watchdog%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20came%20under%20fire%20even%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20expert%20committee%20pointed%20to%20certain%20changes%20in%20rules%20that%20may%20have%