%20he%20carried%20out%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20his%20successful%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20Aizawl%20city.%20The%20four-to-five%20kilometre%20walk%20stretched%20between%20the%20Chanmari%20area%20of%20the%20capital%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20thereafter%2C%20he%20carried%20out%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20being%20more%20%E2%80%9Cinterested%E2%80%9D%20in%20addressing%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20than%20%E2%80%9Cgiving%20importance%E2%80%9D%20to%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20to%20the%20public%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20Modi%20did%20not%20visit%20Manipur%2C%20which%20has%20been%20facing%20ethnic%20strife%20since%20this%20past%20May%2C%20Gandhi%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cshameful%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20country%20not%20to%20visit%20a%20state%20after%20such%20mindless%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20a%20symptom%20of%20the%20problem%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20he%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20minority%20communities%20are%20feeling%20uncomfortable%20and%20there%20is%20oppression%20being%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20people%20of%20India%20under%20its%20rule.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-upcoming-assembly-polls-are-momentous-for-mizorams-political-history%5C%22%3EMizoram%3A%20With%20New%20CM%20Contenders%20in%20Race%2C%20Assembly%20Polls%20to%20Mark%20a%20Break%20from%20the%20Past%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20day%20two%2C%20Gandhi%20addressed%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Aizawl%2C%20where%20he%20was%20asked%20a%20question%20about%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98dynast%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20turn%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20reporter%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20exactly%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Amit%20Shah%20doing%3F%20What%20does%20Rajnath%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20son%20do%3F%20Last%20I%20heard%2C%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20son%20is%20running%20Indian%20cricket.%20Please%20be%20objective.%20Look%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20many%20of%20their%20children%20like%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20are%20%5Bfrom%20political%5D%20dynasties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20was%20also%20seen%20interacting%20with%20the%20local%20public%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20streets%20of%20Aizawl.%20On%20October%2017%2C%20he%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20former%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20Lalthanhalwa.%20Pu%20Hawla%2C%20an%20octogenarian%2C%20is%20a%20veteran%20leader%20from%20the%20state%20who%20is%20not%20contesting%20these%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20returning%20from%20his%20residence%2C%20Gandhi%20hailed%20a%20two-wheeler%20taxi%2C%20a%20popular%20means%20of%20transport%20in%20Aizawl.%20When%20asked%20about%20it%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20experience%20first-hand%20the%20much-talked%20about%20discipline%20followed%20by%20drivers%20in%20Aizawl%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20not%20only%20went%20after%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20two%20national%20leaders%20during%20his%20campaigning%2C%20but%20also%20accused%20the%20ruling%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20and%20the%20new%20regional%20entity%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%2C%20of%20being%20in%20cahoots%20with%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20MNF%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20constituent%20parties%20of%20the%20ZPM%20was%20a%20former%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-ahead-of-polls-mnfs-renewed-call-for-zo-unification-creates-political-flutter%5C%22%3EMizoram%3A%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%2C%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Renewed%20Call%20for%20Zo%20Unification%20Creates%20Political%20Flutter%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20the%20MNF%20and%20ZPM%20as%20%E2%80%9Centry%20points%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20fount%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20these%20two%20political%20parties%2C%20%5Bthe%5D%20MNF%20is%20directly%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20%5Bthe%5D%20ZPM%20is%20not%20fighting%20against%20the%20BJP.%20It%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20entry%20points%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20these%20parties%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinstruments%20of%20%5Ban%5D%20attack%E2%80%9D%20on%20Mizo%20culture%2C%20tradition%20and%20religion%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20his%20party%20believes%20that%20India%20is%20a%20Union%20of%20states%20and%20all%20religions%2C%20cultures%20and%20histories%20should%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20public%20attention%20that%20Gandhi%20grabbed%20in%20Aizawl%20during%20the%20election%20season%2C%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20youth%20wing%20came%20out%20with%20similar%20press%20statements%20on%20October%2017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20bombing%20Mizos%20in%20the%201960s.%20The%20Mizo%20National%20Youth%20Front%20even%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Gandhi%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdevastating%20bombing%E2%80%9D%20carried%20out%20during%20his%20grandmother%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20October%2017%2C%20BJP%20state%20spokesperson%20Lalremsangi%20Fanai%20particularly%20tried%20evoking%20public%20sentiments%20in%20the%20Christian%20majority-state%20by%20accusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20%E2%80%9Csupporting%E2%80%9D%20Hamas%2C%20which%20recently%20attacked%20Israel.%20She%20referred%20to%20Israel%20as%20%E2%80%9CGod%E2%80%99s%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697626819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18155141%2FRagul-in-Mizoram-IV.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-calls-mizo-national-front-instrument-of-bjps-attack-on-mizo-culture-and-tradition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20party's%20candidates%20for%20the%20Mizoram%20elections%20due%20next%20month%20were%20also%20finalised%20during%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20two-day%20visit%20to%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-calls-mizo-national-front-instrument-of-bjps-attack-on-mizo-culture-and-tradition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Jewish%20Advocates%20Turned%20Social%20Media%20Into%20a%20Powerful%20Platform%20for%20Fighting%20Antisemitism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697626800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FColumbia-students-Support-Israel.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235759213%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20influencer%20Lizzy%20Savetsky%20was%20two%20weeks%20into%20filming%20Season%2014%20of%20Bravo%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CReal%20Housewives%20of%20New%20York%E2%80%9D%20when%20a%20tidal%20wave%20of%20antisemitism%20forced%20her%20to%20quit%20the%20show.%20She%20fielded%20death%20threats%20and%20a%20barrage%20of%20online%20harassment.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%20abou