r-of-gaza-hospital-blast%2Famp_articleshow%2F104526743.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sikh%20Man%20Assaulted%20In%20New%20York%20For%20Wearing%20Turban%20In%20Suspected%20Hate%20Crime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20suspected%20incident%20of%20hate%20crime%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20Sikh%20man%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20for%20wearing%20a%20turban%20while%20travelling%20on%20a%20shuttle%20bus.%C2%A0The%20attack%20took%20place%20early%20on%20Sunday%20when%20the%20Sikh%20man%20was%20riding%20a%20shuttle%20bus%20in%20Queens%2C%20a%20borough%20of%20New%20York%20City%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2F-dont-wear-country-man-punches-sikh-teen-turban-nyc-bus-suspected-hate-rcna120571%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Police%20said%20that%20the%20suspect%20was%20riding%20on%20an%20MTA%20bus%20Sunday%20morning%20when%20he%20approached%20a%20male%20passenger%20who%20was%20wearing%20a%20turban%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20wear%20that%20in%20this%20country%20and%20take%20that%20mask%20off!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20then%20punched%20the%20victim%20in%20his%20face%2C%20back%2C%20and%20in%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head%2C%20causing%20cuts%20and%20pain%2C%20according%20to%20police.%C2%A0He%20also%20tried%20to%20remove%20the%20victim's%20turban%20from%20his%20head%20before%20getting%20off%20the%20bus%20and%20leaving%20the%20scene%20on%20foot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20who%20suffered%20a%20minor%20cut%20and%20pain%2C%20refused%20medical%20attention%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sikh%20Coalition%2C%C2%A0a%20national%20Sikh%20faith%20organization%20based%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20it%20was%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20victim%20and%20offering%20him%20support.%20They%20also%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20Facebook%2C%20which%20read%2C%20''The%20Sikh%20Coalition%20is%20aware%20of%20and%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20an%20apparent%20hate-motivated%20attack%20on%20a%20Sikh%20teen%20on%20a%20NYC%20bus%20yesterday.%20Per%20reporting%2C%20the%20assailant%20insulted%20and%20attempted%20to%20tear%20off%20the%20young%20man's%20turban%20and%20punched%20him%20repeatedly.%20We%20are%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20survivor%20and%20working%20with%20him%20to%20provide%20support%20as%20needed%3B%20he%20has%20requested%20anonymity%20for%20the%20time%20being.%20Our%20current%20understanding%20is%20that%20NYPD%20is%2C%20appropriately%2C%20investigating%20this%20incident%20as%20a%20hate%20crime.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20post%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fthesikhcoalition%252Fposts%252Fpfbid02oSgpRUS1gHAeMcH7w8gXAuLnk62cfrXUiAZ8hVwT7VXimHMHxrRyL2rFtzDPKehKl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESikh%20community%20activist%20Japneet%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20''traumatised''%20and%20that%20his%20family%20was%20also%20scared%20for%20him%2C%20according%20to%20ABC7%20television%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Police%20Department's%20hate%20crime%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20police%20on%20Monday%20released%20surveillance%20images%20of%20the%20suspect.%20The%20suspect%20was%20described%20by%20police%20''as%20a%20male%2C%2025-35%20years%20of%20age%2C%20dark%20complexion%2C%20slim%20build%2C%20approximately%205'9%E2%80%B3%20tall%2C%20with%20brown%20eyes%20and%20black%20hair''.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIf%20anybody%20knows%20this%20man%20from%20