0Square%20Puja%20pandal%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20pandal%20had%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20its%20central%20theme.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Santosh%20Mitra%20Square%20Sarbojanin%20Durgotsab%20committee%2C%20known%20for%20organising%20one%20of%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20grandest%20and%20most%20spectacular%20pujas%20every%20year%2C%20has%20promised%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9CAyodhya-like%20atmosphere.%E2%80%9D%20This%20includes%20life-size%20idols%20and%203D%20illuminations%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deities%20Ram%20and%20Hanuman%2C%20and%20the%20recreation%20of%20rituals%20that%20usually%20take%20place%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Saryu%20river%20in%20Ayodhya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20been%20flooded%20with%20images%20of%20the%20pandal%20and%20its%20decorations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20at%20the%20inauguration%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Kolkata%20have%20already%20celebrated%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20temple%E2%80%99s%20inauguration%20through%20this%20Durga%20Puja%20pandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161334%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221178%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161334%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201178w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161334%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x192.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161334%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x655.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22754%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Ayodhya%20Temple%E2%80%99%20at%20Santosh%20Mitra%20Square%20in%20Kolkata.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20communal%20history%20preceding%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20and%20in%20many%20ways%20is%20at%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20the%20world%20a%20mere%20eight%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20Santosh%20Mitra%20Square%20puja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Munshiganj%20in%20Khidirpur%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20a%20modest%20neighbourhood%20are%20worried.%20Their%20concerns%20centre%20around%20unfinished%20pandals%20and%20financial%20constraints%20for%20the%20common%20community%20puja%20they%20organise.%20Communalism%20and%20politics%20are%20missing%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMunshiganj%2C%20located%20in%20Muslim-majority%20area%20of%20Khidirpur%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20red-light%20districts%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20community%20puja%20celebrated%20here%20has%20a%20history%20that%20spans%20decades%2C%20its%20origins%20lost%20to%20memory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20all%20began%20several%20decades%20ago%20when%20the%20Muslim%20neighbours%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20few%20Hindu%20families%20residing%20here%2C%20determined%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20was%20left%20out%20of%20the%20celebration.%20Muslims%20residents%20call%20the%20goddess%20%E2%80%98ma%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganised%20by%20the%20local%20Five%20Star%20Club%2C%20this%20Puja%20lacks%20the%20grandeur%20typically%20associated%20with%20community%20pujas%20in%20Kolkata.%20While%20the%20larger%20pujas%20like%20Santosh%20Mitra%20Square%2C%20have%20already%20drawn%20thousands%20of%20visitors%2C%20the%20small%20pandal%20at%20Munshiganj%2C%20devoid%20of%20intricate%20artistry%20or%20a%20specific%20theme%2C%20is%20still%20under%20construction.%20With%20Durga%20Puja%20only%20a%20few%20days%20away%2C%20Mirza%20Saifudding%20Baig%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20puja%20organising%20committee%2C%20is%20visibly%20anxious.%20Every%20evening%20after%20work%2C%20Saifuddin%20Baig%20meets%20with%20Latif%2C%20Al%20Amin%2C%20Joy%2C%20and%20others%20to%20inspect%20the%20pandal%E2%80%99s%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x215.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x733.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Munshiganj%20pandal%2C%20being%20organised%20by%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20festival%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20We%20all%20live%20here.%20Ram%20Pal%2C%20our%20local%20potter%20makes%20the%20idol.%20Joy%20and%20Bikash%20look%20after%20the%20ritual%20part.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20mohalla%20contributes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3ESex%20workers%20in%20the%20locality%20send%20donations.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20take%20part%20in%20the%20puja%20despite%20our%20requests%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammad%20Latif%2C%20a%20key%20organiser.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%