ut%20of%20the%20celebration.%20Muslims%20residents%20call%20the%20goddess%20%E2%80%98ma%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganised%20by%20the%20local%20Five%20Star%20Club%2C%20this%20Puja%20lacks%20the%20grandeur%20typically%20associated%20with%20community%20pujas%20in%20Kolkata.%20While%20the%20larger%20pujas%20like%20Santosh%20Mitra%20Square%2C%20have%20already%20drawn%20thousands%20of%20visitors%2C%20the%20small%20pandal%20at%20Munshiganj%2C%20devoid%20of%20intricate%20artistry%20or%20a%20specific%20theme%2C%20is%20still%20under%20construction.%20With%20Durga%20Puja%20only%20a%20few%20days%20away%2C%20Mirza%20Saifudding%20Baig%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20puja%20organising%20committee%2C%20is%20visibly%20anxious.%20Every%20evening%20after%20work%2C%20Saifuddin%20Baig%20meets%20with%20Latif%2C%20Al%20Amin%2C%20Joy%2C%20and%20others%20to%20inspect%20the%20pandal%E2%80%99s%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x215.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161425%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.40%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x733.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Munshiganj%20pandal%2C%20being%20organised%20by%2