Modi%20is%20an%20incredibly%20popular%20leader%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20today%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20perhaps%20no%20place%20but%20Ahmedabad%20that%20he%20can%20entirely%20count%20on%20to%20deliver%20to%20perfection%20everything%20that%20he%20needs.%20The%20waters%20had%20already%20been%20tested%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20had%20been%20invited%20at%20this%20venue%20on%20March%209%20before%20the%20start%20of%20an%20India-Australia%20test%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPacking%20the%20stands%20for%20test%20cricket%20in%20India%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20easiest%20of%20jobs.%20To%20stage%20a%20political%20event%20that%20looks%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20music%20concert%20required%20not%20only%20for%20the%20stands%20to%20look%20reasonably%20full%20but%20also%20for%20the%20crowd%20to%20uniformly%20act%20obsequious%20and%20indebted%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20their%20leader.%20Individually%20vetting%20the%20thousands%20you%E2%80%99ve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Frevealed-why-tickets-for-day-1-of-4th-ind-aus-test-in-ahmedabad-are-locked-out-leaving-fans-disheartened-article-98405395%5C%22%3Edistributed%20free%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E%20amongst%20is%20impossible%2C%20even%20for%20a%20party%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20resources.%20The%20safer%20option%20is%20to%20stage%20it%20among%20a%20people%20you%20have%20complete%20confidence%20in%20to%20not%20spoil%20your%20script.%20This%20is%20where%20Ahmedabad%20can%20be%20blindly%20banked%20upon%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20deliver%20Ahmedabad%20did%2C%20to%20perfection%2C%20as%20Modi%20and%20Albanese%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-australian-pm-anthony-albanese-to-watch-india-australia-test-in-gujarat-today-3845277%5C%22%3Erode%20on%20a%20chariot%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20ground%20taking%20a%20lap%20of%20honour%20to%20rapturous%20reception%20of%20a%20crowd%20(far%20from%20capacity%20despite%20the%20best%20efforts)%20just%20too%20grateful%20to%20be%20breathing%20the%20same%20air%20the%20man%20they%E2%80%99ve%20submitted%20their%20ability%20to%20reason%20for%20did.%20It%20was%20pretty%20emblematic%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98new%20India%E2%80%99%20where%20staged%20events%20with%20vetted%20audience%20in%20attendance%20inflating%20the%20ego%20of%20an%20elected%20leader%20is%20how%20national%20pride%20is%20measured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECricket%20has%20willingly%20allowed%20itself%20to%20be%20used%20as%20a%20vehicle%20facilitating%20this%20pomposity%20and%20the%20gigantic%20bowl%20in%20Ahmedabad%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%3A%20The%20Good%20and%20the%20Ugly%20of%20a%20Hysterical%20Crowd%E2%80%99s%20Collective%20Energy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-world-cup-hysterical-crowd-collective-energy%5C%22%3ECricket%20World%20Cup%3A%20The%20Good%20and%20the%20Ugly%20of%20a%20Hysterical%20Crowd%E2%80%99s%20Collective%20Energy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20when%20India%20hosted%20Pakistan%20at%20this%20stadium%20though%2C%20the%20vast%20sea%20of%20orange%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20meant%20to%20be%20as%20conspicuous%20as%20it%20looked%20on%20the%20drone%20shots.%20Much%20of%20the%20sitting%20area%2C%20already%20expected%20to%20have%20turned%20blue%20by%20the%20time%20of%20toss%2C%20remained%20unoccupied%20well%20past%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stands%20eventually%20did%20fill%20considerably%2C%20though%20the%20broadcasters%20refrained%20from%20repeatedly%20boasting%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98record%20number%E2%80%99%20of%20people%20gathered%20for%20a%20cricket%20match.%20Which%20is%20probably%20an%20indication%20the%20number%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20the%20one%20they%20were%20desperately%20craving%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20anticipation%20built%20around%20this%20game%20was%20somewhat%20rooted%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20Pakistan%20attempted%20some%20rabble-rousing.%20Both%20the%20cricket%20boards%20have%20been%20at%20diplomatic%20loggerheads%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20India%E2%80%99s%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20didn%E2%80%99t%20change%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20last%20month%20and%20that%20left%20the%20hosts%20justifiably%20aggrieved.%20Having%20to%20come%20across%20as%20not%20taking%20things%20lying%20down%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20had%20at%20one%20point%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fstory%2Fpakistan-wont-play-world-cup-if-india-do-not-come-for-asia-cup-pcb-chief-2301883-2022-11-26%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520Short%26amp%3Btext%3DPakistan%2520Cricket%2520Board%2520(PCB)%2520chief%2Cover%2520World%2520Cup%2520next%2520year.%5C%22%3Ethreatened%20to%20reciprocate%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20not%20showing%20up%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20but%20few%20treated%20it%20with%20any%20seriousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%20is%20to%20not%20extend%20cricketing%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20beyond%20multilateral%20tournaments.%20The%20board%20of%20course%20does%20not%20have%20the%20autonomy%20to%20decide%20this%20on%20its%20own%20and%20must%20adhere%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20directives.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20element%20of%20subterfuge%20here%3B%20in%20that%2C%20the%20BCCI%20likes%20to%20pose%20as%20if%20it%20plays%20Pakistan%20in%20these%20international%20events%20only%20out%20of%20fulfilling%20its%20commitment%20despite%20the%20strongest%20reservations.%20But%20this%20could%20not%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20has%20affirmed%20a%20very%20uncompromising%20and%20principled%20stand%2C%20when%20it%20actually%20comes%20to%20milking%20the%20popularity%20of%20an%20India-Pakistan%20match%2C%20the%20BCCI%20and%20its%20entire%20ecosystem%20that%20feeds%20off%20cricket%20cares%20little%20about%20those%20principles.%20Tournament%20after%20tournament%2C%20formats%20and%20schedules%20are%20rigged%20to%20maximise%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20two%20teams%20facing%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20broadcasters%20in%20India%20have%20no%20hesitation%20building%20up%20the%20game%20as%20the%20ultimate%20cultural%20marker%20of%20an%20entire%20nation.%20A%20slew%20of%20news%20anchors%20and%20former%20cricketers%20who%E2%80%99ve%20carved%20a%20brand%20out%20of%20insincerely%20rehashing%20hawkish%20jargon%20on%20TV%20are%20all%20too%20happy%20to%20be%20sharing%20screen-space%20with%20their%20Pakistani%20counterparts.%20And%20then%20follows%20the%20same%20tired%20rhetoric%20of%20sports%20having%20to%20rise%20above%20the%20ugliness%20of%20daily%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20BCCI%20ascribes%20a%20first-among-equals%20status%20to%20an%20India-Pakistan%20contest%20was%20confirmed%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20itself%20when%20a%20special%20reserve%20day%20was%20arranged%20for%20it%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20washout.%20None%20of%20the%20other%20teams%20had%20their%20games%20insured%20by%20such%20an%20arrangement%20and%20worse%20still%2C%20they%20were%20made%20to%20publicly%20state%20they%20were%20on%20board%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20treatment%20for%20this%20fixture%20only%20became%20more%20blatant%20on%20Saturday%20when%20a%20haphazardly%20organised%20pre-game%20entertainment%20show%20was%20arranged%20ahead%20of%20the%20match.%C2%A0%20Featuring%20some%20of%20the%20more%20famous%20names%20in%20the%20Indian%20music%20industry%2C%20the%20show%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20the%20perfect%20precursor%20before%20the%20showdown%20event%20in%20front%20of%20a%20record%20crowd.%20It%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20another%20world%20event%20across%20all%20sports%20that%20commences%20without%20an%20opening%20ceremony%20but%20then%20has%20one%20specially%20arranged%20for%20a%20blockbuster%20game%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20it%20was%20the%20backlash%20they%20faced%20for%20this%20brazenness%20or%20maybe%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20poor%20due%20diligence%20where%20someone%20forgot%20to%20clarify%20who%20pays%20royalty%20fees%20to%20the%20music%20labels%2C%20but%20minutes%20after%2C%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20show%20began%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20for%20the%20live%20audience%20in%20the%20stadium%20and%20that%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20televised.%20Nothing%20could%E2%80%99ve%20summed%20up%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20ineptitude%2C%20chicanery%2C%20and%20all-round%20clumsiness%20more%20poetically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20is%20wide%20open%20still%20and%20odds%20aren%E2%80%99t%20totally%20stacked%20against%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20locking%20a%20faceoff%20in%20the%20final%20at%20the%20same%20venue.%20Who%20knows%2C%20it%20might%20even%20prompt%20the%20BCCI%20into%20arranging%20a%20closing%20ceremony%20for%20the%20tournament%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShould%20it%20really%20materialise%20though%2C%20no%20one%20is%20going%20to%20be%20happier%20than%20the%20BCCI.%20The%20political%20imagery%20of%20India%20defeating%20Pakistan%20to%20lift%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20ultimate%20prize%20in%20a%20stadium%20named%20after%20%E2%80%93%20and%20perhaps%20even%20in%20presence%20of%20%E2%80%93%20its%20tallest%20active%20politician%20is%20massive%3B%20particularly%20six%20months%20before%20the%20country%20goes%20to%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20India%20lifted%20a%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%20the%20visuals%20of%20a%20jampacked%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20jamming%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2FGyhPAE58FR4%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVande%20Matram%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20chorus%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20for%20a%20memory%20everyone%20went%20home%20with.%20The%20scenes%20might%20very%20well%20repeat%20in%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20time%20but%20Ahmedabad%20may%20have%20a%20slightly%20different%20choice%20of%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stadium%20has%20in%20a%20short%20time%20managed%20to%20shift%20the%20fan%20culture%20to%20be%20more%20representative%20of%20the%20politics%20its%20benefactors%20stand%20for.%20Politically%20loaded%20religious%20sloganeering%20is%20getting%20increasingly%20common.%20The%20familiar%20%3Cem%3EBharat%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EVande%20Matram%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20now%20followed%20with%20the%20even%20more%20affirmatively%20raised%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20an%20innocuous%20invocation%20of%20faith.%20During%20the%20India-Australia%20test%20in%20March%2C%20the%20chants%20were%20directed%20at%20Indian%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.com%2Fsports%2Ffans-chant-jai-shree-ram-in-front-of-mohammed-shami-during-4th-test-between-ind-aus-at-ahmedabad-video-goes-viral-watch-5938124%2F%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E.%20No%20one%20chose%20to%20address%20it%20then%20and%20this%20time%20the%20Pakistani%20batsman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket-news%2Findia-vs-pakistan-fans-taunt-muhammad-rizwan-with-jai-shri-ram-chants-politicians-call-it-unacceptable-11697362408544.html%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Rizwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22India-Pakistan%20Cricket%3A%20On%20a%20Sticky%20Wicket%20in%20Ahmedabad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-pakistan-cricket-on-a-sticky-wicket-in-ahmedabad%5C%22%3EIndia-Pakistan%20Cricket%3A%20On%20a%20Sticky%20Wicket%20in%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20back%2C%20former%20PCB%20chairman%20Najam%20Sethi%20had%20voiced%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomic