ent%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elike%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewill%20have%20to%20delay%20its%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20calls%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20vortex%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20says%20simply%20having%20a%20plan%20can%20help%20Americans%20find%20their%20way%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20new%20surveys%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmanpfm.com%2Finvestment-blog%2Fnavigating-the-financial-vortex%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankrate.com%2Ff%2F102997%2Fx%2F5c5f81c29a%2Fseptember-2023-fsp-press-release-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBankrate%3C%2Fa%3E%20examined%20how%20confident%20people%20feel%20about%20their%20retirement.%20While%20most%20have%20a%20dim%20outlook%2C%20the%20results%20varied%20by%20age%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20had%20a%20financial%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bankrate's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAugust%20survey%20of%202%2C527%20US%20adults%20working%20full-time%2C%20part-time%2C%20or%20temporarily%20unemployed%2C%2056%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20feel%20behind%20on%20their%20retirement%20savings%2C%20and%2037%25%20believe%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20this%20was%20broken%20down%20by%20generations%2C%20the%20results%20showed%20that%20older%20people%20were%20much%20more%20worried%20about%20their%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Xers%2C%20aged%2043-58%2C%20are%20the%20most%20worried%2C%20with%2069%25%20feeling%20behind%20on%20their%20retirement%20savings.%20Baby%20boomers%2C%20aged%2059-77%2C%20were%20next%20at%2060%25.%20For%20younger%20adults%2C%20fewer%20than%20half%20were%20worried%2C%20with%2049%25%20of%20millennials%2C%20aged%2027-42%2C%20and%2042%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20aged%2018-26%2C%20fearing%20they%20are%20not%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smiling%20young%20man%20looks%20at%20his%20cell%20phone%20with%20a%20colorful%20city%20street%20behind%20him%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b6b2911ccd1e00198aa166%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20feel%20they%20are%20on%20track%20financially%20for%20retirement.%3Cp%3EHinterhaus%20Productions%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20pressures%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20vortex%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20meeting%20retirement%20goals%20is%20due%20in%20large%20part%20to%20what%20Goldman%20Sachs%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20vortex%26quot%3B%20of%20competing%20priorities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20have%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20notes%20that%20people%20struggle%20to%20balance%20multiple%20financial%20goals%20with%20limited%20financial%20resources.%20Money%20that%20would%20go%20to%20retirement%20savings%20is%20also%20being%20tugged%20into%20the%20financial%20vortex%20by%20things%20like%20credit%20card%20debt%2C%20student%20loans%2C%20college%2C%20care%20for%20children%20and%20older%20adults%2C%20and%20financial%20hardships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20their%20survey%20of%205%2C261%20US%20participants%20in%20June%20and%20July%2C%20using%20a%20financial%20plan%20has%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20how%20confident%20people%20are%20that%20they%20will%20meet%20their%20retirement%20needs%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20with%20a%20plan%2C%2079%25%20of%20respondents%20are%20on%20track%20or%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20for%20retirement.%20Meanwhile%2C%20only%2034%25%20of%20people%20without%20a%20plan%20had%20the%20same%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%2060%25%20of%20those%20surveyed%20had%20at%20least%20a%20basic%20plan%20for%20how%20much%20retirement%20savings%20they%20need%20and%20how%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Older%20couple%20at%20a%20table%20in%20front%20of%20a%20laptop%20talking%20through%20personal%20finance%20together.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b2eba12dc4f001a175cf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20confident%20in%20their%20retirement%20hopes%20if%20they%20have%20a%20plan.%3Cp%3EDrazen%20Zigic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20also%20expressed%20concern%20for%20the%20level%20of%20financial%20literacy%20among%20the%20respondents.%20Nearly%20half%2C%2047%25%2C%20are%20self-managing%20their%20retirement%20savings%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20when%20the%20respondents%20were%20given%20a%20five-question%20financial%20literacy%20quiz%2C%20only%2013%25%20got%20all%20five%20answers%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%2020%25%20of%20respondents%20believe%20they%20will%20have%20to%20delay%20their%20retirement%20by%20at%20least%20four%20years%2C%20and%2060%25%20said%20it%20will%20be%20pushed%20back%20at%20least%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20falling%20behind%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said%20the%20two%20biggest%20factors%20that%20can%20help%20people%20reach%20their%20retirement%20goals%20are%20increasing%20financial%20literacy%20and%20having%20a%20personalized%20financial%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20manage%20the%20complexity%20and%20financial%20uncertainty%20of%20retirement%20without%20those%20things%20will%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-savings-investing-goldman-sachs-financial-advice-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697623861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652e93546561dd877e7c4335%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin