C%20gaping%20wounds%20are%20exposing%20a%20gaping%20global%20power%20vacuum.%20Tectonic%20shifts%20are%20in%20motion%20not%20just%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20but%20in%20the%20geopolitical%20chessboard%20in%20real-time.%20With%20the%20recent%20horrific%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20innocent%20lives%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20amorphous%20fault%20lines%20have%20been%20forced%20into%20clear%20lines.%20But%20silence%20is%20acquiescence%2C%20and%20the%20delayed%20and%20deafening%20one%20from%20China%20and%20Russia%20seems%20to%20aim%20at%20one%20goal%20-%20undermine%20America's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20where%20the%20Jewish%20population%20is%20more%20than%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20Jerusalem%20combined%2C%20and%20which%20has%20been%20the%20center%20for%20rallies%20this%20last%20week%2C%20the%20emotional%20flooding%20has%20overwhelmed%20both%20university%20campuses%20and%20personal%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reflects%20the%20conundrum%20the%20US%20currently%20finds%20itself%20in.%20It%20is%20argued%20that%20Israel%20has%20an%20inordinate%20impact%20on%20US%20foreign%20policy%2C%20making%20it%20partisan%20in%20this%20long-standing%20dispute.%20But%20one%20must%20objectively%20understand%20the%20contribution%20of%20Jewish%20Americans%20to%20America's%20success%20over%20the%20last%20100%20years.%20From%20Wall%20Street%20to%20technology%20to%20health%20care%20to%20cutting-edge%20research%20in%20academia%2C%20Jewish%20Americans%20have%20had%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20America's%20rise.%20So%20how%20can%20America%20not%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20very%20people%20who%20have%20been%20pivotal%20to%20its%20success%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20however%2C%20makes%20the%20Arab%20states%20view%20it%20as%20partisan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELong-term%20American%20policymakers%20believe%20oil%20will%20have%20declining%20relevance%20over%20the%20next%20few%20decades%2C%20as%20clean%20energy%20alternatives%20emerge%2C%20subduing%20the%20global%20ramifications%20of%20Middle%20East%20tensions.%20But%2C%20as%20this%20recent%20tragedy%20shows%2C%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20they%20have%20been%20blindsided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20current%20focus%20is%20firmly%20on%20China%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20US%20interests%20globally.%20It%20is%20also%20helping%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20battle%20against%20an%20expansionist%20Putin.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20does%20not%20want%20a%20Jimmy%20Carter%20redux%2C%20is%20struggling%20with%2054%25%20disapproval%20ratings.%20He%20is%20trying%20very%20hard%20to%20show%20he%20has%20things%20under%20control.%20America's%20plate%20is%20currently%20clearly%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%2C%20despite%20its%20historical%20relevance%2C%20is%20losing%20strategic%20and%20economic%20depth%2C%20and%20without%20Angela%20Merkel%20-%20considered%20the%20only%20grown-up%20in%20the%20room%20-%20it%20lacks%20political%20will%20and%20cohesion.%20Russia%2C%20which%20managed%20a%20high-wire%20act%20between%20the%20Arab%20States%20and%20Israel%2C%20is%20slowly%20going%20into%20China's%20orbit%2C%20and%20through%20that%2C%20forming%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20Iran.%20The%20instability%20of%20war%20also%20benefits%20Russia%2C%20because%20of%20its%20economy's%20correlation%20to%20oil%20and%20arms%20exports%20and%20a%20deflection%20to%20its%20own%20battle%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina's%20foreign%20policy%20is%20dictated%20by%20Confucianism%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20extremely%20pragmatic%20in%20its%20approach.%20It%20does%20not%20like%20to%20get%20deeply%20involved%20in%20any%20dispute%20unless%20it%20provides%20material%20benefits%20to%20its%20national%20interests.%20China's%20eye%20on%20Taiwan%20due%20to%20its%20high-end%20semiconductor%20facilities%20and%20US%20attempts%20to%20thwart%20those%20efforts%20make%20this%20Middle%20East%20conflict%20a%20convenient%20global%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20is%20the%20last%20peace%20broker%20in%20the%20region.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Washington%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20even%20though%20the%20majority%20of%20Saudis%20want%20to%20do%20business%20with%20Israelis%20irrespective%20of%20conflict%2C%20they%20prioritise%20a%20religious%20agenda%2C%20with%20the%20Al%20Aqsa%20mosque%20being%20at%20the%20center%2C%20over%20Palestinian%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20of%20global%20leadership%20is%20searching%20for%20a%20peacemaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20historically%20has%20had%20a%20very%20good%20relationship%20with%20the%20Arab%20nations%20and%20has%20a%20large%20expat%20population%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20-%20given%20that%20its%20Muslim%20population%20is%20almost%20equal%20to%2033%20members%20of%20the%20organisation%20-%20were%20it%20not%20for%20Pakistan.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20historical%20relationship%20with%20Iran%20going%20back%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20a%20country%20that%20was%20its%20neighbour%20until%201947.%20Importantly%2C%20India%20has%20been%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20hosts%20a%20Palestinian%20ambassador%2C%20and%20has%20supported%20many%20UN%20resolutions%20over%20the%20years%20calling%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20interviewed%20Saudi%20Princess%20Basma%20Bint%20Saud%2C%20I%20remember%20her%20saying%20India's%20potential%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20needs%20to%20be%20leveraged.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20so%20much%20in%20common%20-%20the%20way%20we%20look%2C%20what%20we%20eat%2C%20and%20our%20culture%2C%20and%20it%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20invest%20in%20something%20you%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20The%20longstanding%20Ganga-Jamuni%20Tehzeeb%20is%20an%20asset%20that%20carries%20diplomatic%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20a%20deep%20and%20ideological%20bond%20with%20Israeli%20PM%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20and%20the%20two%20call%20each%20other%20close%20friends.%20Modi%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20global%20leaders%20to%20unequivocally%20condemn%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20speak%20directly%20to%20Bibi%2C%20and%20offer%20unconditional%20support.%20New%20Delhi%20wants%20the%20recently%20announced%20India-Middle%20East%20economic%20corridor%20to%20become%20a%20reality.%20The%20ambitious%20project%20will%20connect%20the%20Arab%20states%2C%20Israel%2C%20and%20Europe%20with%20India%20economically%20and%20strategically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20asserted%20itself%20in%20difficult%20geopolitical%20conflicts%20in%20recent%20years.%20With%20the%20purchase%20of%20Russian%20oil%20during%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20it%20has%20shown%20it%20can%20adroitly%20manage%20the%20global%20diplomatic%20tightrope.%20With%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20G20%20summit%2C%20India%20demonstrated%20it%20can%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20significant%20%26quot%3Bgeopolitical%20trust%20capital%26quot%3B%20has%20taken%20decades%20of%20careful%20diplomacy%20and%20intricate%20relationships%20to%20cultivate.%20This%20accrued%20capital%20can%20be%20used%20to%20facilitate%20the%20unthinkable%20-%20lasting%20Middle%20East%20peace.%20Once%20the%20bombs%20stop%20dropping%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20will%20not%20listen%20to%20each%20other%20but%20might%20listen%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20to%20be%20in%20that%20room%2C%20because%20if%20not%20so%2C%20who%20will%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Namrata%20Brar%20is%20an%20Indian-American%20journalist%2C%20investigative%20reporter%2C%20and%20news%20anchor.%20She%20is%20the%20former%20US%20bureau%20chief%20of%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2F