.com%2Fretirement-plans-most-generous-countries-best-places-to-retire-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Convicted%20For%20Murder%20Of%20Journalist%20Soumya%20Vishwanathan%20In%20Delhi%20In%202008%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFive%20people%20were%20today%20convicted%20in%20the%202008%20murder%20case%20of%20journalist%20Soumya%20Vishwanathan.%20A%20Delhi%20court%20also%20held%20the%20accused%20guilty%20of%20loot%20and%20under%20provisions%20of%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20Kapoor%2C%20Amit%20Shukla%2C%20Baljit%20Mallick%20and%20Akshay%20Kumar%20were%20held%20guilty%20of%20murder%20and%20loot.%20The%20fifth%20accused%2C%20Ajay%20Sethi%2C%20was%20held%20guilty%20of%20helping%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoumya%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20journalist%20with%20Headlines%20Today%2C%20was%20killed%20at%20Delhi's%20Vasant%20Vihar%20on%20September%2030%2C%202008%20while%20she%20was%20on%20her%20way%20back%20from%20work.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20in%20her%20car.%20She%20had%20suffered%20a%20headshot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20after%20the%20judgment%2C%20Soumya's%20mother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20our%20daughter%2C%20but%20this%20will%20act%20as%20a%20deterrent%20for%20others.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20wants%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice's%20first%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20case%20came%20while%20it%20was%20investigating%20another%20murder%20case%20-%20that%20of%20IT%20executive%20Jigisha%20Ghose%2C%20found%20dead%20in%20Faridabad%20months%20after%20Soumya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKapoor%2C%20Shukla%20and%20Malik%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20IT%20executive's%20death.%20During%20questioning%2C%20police%20found%20their%20links%20with%20the%20Vasant%20Vihar%20murder.%20Thereafter%2C%20two%20more%20accused%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20620-pa