ant%20to%20keep%20distinguishing%20between%20interactions%20with%20AI%20and%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20named%20it%20ChatGPT%20and%20not%20a%20person's%20name%20very%20intentionally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Altman.%20He%20added%20that%20OpenAI%20makes%20it%20clear%20to%20users%20that%20they%20aren't%20talking%20to%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman's%20comments%20come%20amid%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20AI%20companies%20putting%20out%20chatbots%20with%20human-like%20personality%20and%20friendliness%20as%20a%20key%20feature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20Anthropic%20AI's%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F7%2F11%2F23790254%2Fanthropic-claude-chatbot-ai-available-beta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bfriendly%26quot%3B%20chatbot%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Character.AI's%20chatbots%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacterai-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-mimics-mario-elon-musk-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euser-created%20personalities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Meta's%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chatbots-assistants-tom-brady-mr-beast-kendall-jenner-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrity%20AI%20assistants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20backstories%20and%20use%20the%20likeness%20of%20public%20figures%20like%20Kendall%20Jenner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20AI%20assistant%20is%20called%20Meta%20AI.%20It's%20similarly%20neutral%20and%20has%20a%20neutral%20tone%20and%20has%20a%20neutral%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Cox%2C%20Meta's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20response%20to%20Altman's%20comments%20at%20a%20separate%20interview%20during%20the%20same%20event.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20also%20think%20there's%20room%20for%20more%20expression%20and%20more%20playfulness%20in%20what's%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Altman%20isn't%20alone%20in%20his%20concern%20about%20humans%20bonding%20with%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20tend%20to%20anthropomorphize%20%E2%80%94%20or%20attach%20human%20qualities%20%E2%80%94%20to%20objects%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20published%20by%20the%20think%20tank%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizen.org%2Farticle%2Fchatbots-are-not-people-dangerous-human-like-anthropomorphic-ai-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPublic%20Citizen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20warned%20that%20companies%20deploying%20chatbots%20could%20exploit%20users'%20trust%20and%20manipulate%20their%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20reported%20by%20Insider's%20Rob%20Price%2C%20there%20are%20ethical%20concerns%20over%20users%20getting%20attached%20to%20their%20chatbots.%20When%20AI%20startup%20Replika%20disabled%20their%20chatbots'%20%26quot%3Berotic%20role-play%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-your-ai-says-she-loves-you-2023-10%5C%22%3Ecaused%20an%20uproar%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20users%20who%20felt%20their%20AI%20companions%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Blobotomized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20Altman%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-misgivings-friendships-ai-personality-chatbots-openai-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697621874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f7e1696f7540cd05f0938%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-misgivings-friendships-ai-personality-chatbots-openai-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20named%20it%20ChatGPT%20a