20Breckenridge%2C%20Colorado%2C%20for%20the%20active%20lifestyle%2C%20but%20chose%20to%20leave%20because%20it%20was%20too%20expensive.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Callie%20Kuchan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECallie%20Kuchan%20is%20returning%20to%20Illinois%20after%20finding%20a%20small%20ski%20town%20in%20Colorado%20too%20expensive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKuchan%20lived%20in%20Breckenridge%20for%20four%20years%20and%20wanted%20to%20stay%2C%20but%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20buy%20a%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20also%20said%20the%20mountain%20has%20gotten%20too%20crowded%20since%20Covid%2C%20and%20it's%20too%20hard%20to%20make%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Callie%20Kuchan%2C%2031%2C%20about%20her%20decision%20to%20leave%20Breckenridge%2C%20Colorado%2C%20a%20ski%20town%2080%20miles%20outside%20of%20Denver%2C%20and%20return%20to%20her%20hometown%20to%20Chicago%2C%20Illinois%2C%20with%20her%20husband.%20She%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40calliejustinewrites%2Fvideo%2F7281720645786848555%3F_r%3D1%26_t%3D8gRxtue7EQU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eposted%20about%20the%20decision%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20from%20suburban%20Chicago%20and%20moved%20to%20Colorado%20in%202018.%20I%20lived%20in%20Denver%20for%20a%20year%2C%20and%20then%20I%20moved%20up%20to%20Breckenridge%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Breckenridge%20for%20lifestyle.%20To%20hike%2C%20bike%2C%20ski%2C%20cross-country%20ski%20%E2%80%94%20pretty%20much%20all%20of%20the%20outdoor%20sports%20that%20I%20could%20get%20myself%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20one%20thing%20that%20I%20think%20is%20amazing%20about%20living%20there%20is%20just%20having%20the%20mountains%20in%20your%20backyard.%20I%20lived%20where%20people%20vacation%20and%20spend%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20and%20I%20definitely%20tried%20to%20not%20take%20that%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20definitely%20is%20that%20element%20of%20everyone%20around%20you%20is%20on%20vacation%20and%20you're%20not.%20You're%20living%20your%20mundane%20life%20while%20being%20surrounded%20by%20that%20environment%2C%20which%20can%20be%20challenging%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20element%20of%20living%20in%20Colorado%20and%20having%20the%20access%20to%20all%20of%20these%20things%20that%20don't%20make%20them%20as%20glamorous%20anymore.%20I%20love%20skiing%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20excitement%20for%20skiing%20as%20I%20did%20when%20I%20would%20go%20on%20my%20yearly%20ski%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreckenridge%20is%20too%20expensive%20to%20live%20comfortably%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lived%20in%20a%20two-bedroom%20condo%2C%20and%20know%20the%20owner%20who%20gave%20us%20a%20wonderful%20deal.%20Our%20rent%20was%20raised%20one%20time%20while%20living%20there%20in%20the%20four%20years%2C%20but%20was%20still%20under%20%243%2C000%20a%20month.%20We%20probably%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20live%20there%20without%20this%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20definitely%20had%20the%20mindset%20for%20most%20of%20my%20time%20living%20there%20that%20I%20will%20live%20there%20forever.%20When%20I%20first%20moved%20there%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20at%20real%20estate%20to%20buy%20and%20it%20was%20more%20expensive%20than%20other%20places%2C%20like%20Chicago%20or%20Denver%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20relatively%20affordable%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20%2460%2C000.%20I%20was%20working%20as%20an%20account%20manager%20in%20the%20hospitality%20sector%20for%20a%20ski%20resort%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20Covid%2C%20the%20real%20estate's%20just%20been%20astronomical.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20the%20smallest%2C%20crappiest%20house%20that%20I%20could%20find%20in%20the%20area%2C%20it%20would%20be%20in%20the%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20poses%20with%20her%20dog%20on%20top%20of%20a%20mountain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ed764211def8ed837789c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECallie%20Kuchan%20moved%20to%20Breckenridge%2C%20Colorado%2C%20for%20the%20active%20lifestyle%2C%20but%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20live%20how%20she%20wanted%20to.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Callie%20Kuchan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20three%20jobs%20to%20try%20to%20save%20up%20some%20money%20to%20put%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20house.%20I%20was%20always%20looking%20at%20the%20market%20to%20see%20when%20I%20could%20swoop%20in%20and%20buy%20something.%20I%20convinced%20myself%20that%20I%20would%20be%20okay%20living%20in%20a%20tiny%20apartment.%20I%20just%20saw%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20that%20it%20wasn't%20possible%20long-term%2C%20affordability-wise%20working%20in%20the%20ski%20industry.%20Without%20wanting%20to%20leave%2C%20I%20started%20noticing%20last%20winter%20I%20started%20getting%20a%20little%20burnt%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20don't%20necessarily%20need%20a%20fancy%20home%2C%20but%20we%20definitely%20wanted%20to%20get%20as%20much%20bang%20for%20our%20buck%20as%20we%20possibly%20could.%20I%20would%20have%20been%20comfortable%20buying%20a%20home%20for%20under%20%24600%2C000%20with%20my%20spouse.%20In%20Breckenridge%2C%20you%20would%20get%20a%20tiny%2C%20tiny%20condo.%20In%20the%20Chicago%20area%2C%20you%20could%20get%20a%20house%20with%20a%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20were%20going%20to%20spend%20this%20amount%20of%20money%20for%20a%20place%20to%20live%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20get%20more%20bang%20for%20our%20buck.%20We%20didn't%20necessarily%20need%20something%20big%2C%20but%20we%20were%20quickly%20outgrowing%20our%20900-square-foot%20condo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conclusion%20that%20we%20came%20to%20is%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20explore%20other%20options.%20We%20moved%20into%20a%20four-bedroom%20home%20in%20suburban%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20wasn't%20just%20the%20housing%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20the%20slopes%20have%20become%20way%20too%20crowded%20to%20enjoy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Covid%20hit%2C%20there%20was%20literally%20nowhere%20to%20go%20and%20you%20couldn't%20do%20anything%20that%20wasn't%20outside.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20drove%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20to%20go%20places%20like%20ski%20resorts%20and%20national%20parks.%20So%20the%20amount%20of%20people%20at%20the%20resort%20skiing%20has%20been%20just%20astronomical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20a%20typical%20desk%20job%20Monday%20through%20Friday%2C%20so%20I%20can't%20ski%20during%20the%20week.%20So%20on%20the%20weekends%20I'm%20skiing%20when%20everyone's%20on%20their%20weekend%20trips%2C%20when%20everyone%20is%20coming%20up%20from%20Denver%20for%20the%20day%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20insanely%20crowded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20ski%20mountain%20at%20dusk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ed86bbe9edfa8eda30c70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBreckenridge%2C%20Colorado.%3Cp%3Edarekm101%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20describe%20it%20as%20people%20playing%20%26quot%3BFrogger.%26quot%3B%20You%20don't%20actually%20get%20to%20ski%2C%20you're%20just%20dodging%20people.%20So%20I%20definitely%20have%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20it%20may%20be%20better%20for%20me%20to%20live%20in%20a%20different%20place%20and%20vacation%20and%20get%20more%20skiing%20in%20because%20I%20skip%20days%20of%20skiing%20because%20it's%20so%20crowded%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20wait%2020%20or%2030%20minutes%20in%20a%20lift%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20seasonality%20of%20the%20work%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20have%20long-lasting%20connections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECommunity%20is%20the%20best%20and%20worst%20thing%20about%20living%20in%20Breckenridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20around%20a%20lot%20of%20like-minded%20people%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20very%20well-traveled%20people%2C%20adventurous%20free-spirit%20people%20that%20I%20really%20enjoy%20being%20around%20that%20don't%20take%20life%20too%20seriously%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20as%20serious%20as%20living%20in%20a%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20people%20are%20very%20transient.%20So%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20move%20to%20mountain%20towns%20for%20a%20season%2C%20for%20a%20year%2C%20or%20until%20they%20get%20kicked%20out%20because%20of%20the%20affordability%20or%20lack%20of%20job%20opportunities.%20So%20it's%20hard%20to%20have%20a%20community%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20make%20friends%2C%20especially%20for%20someone%20in%20my%20age%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20poses%20in%20Chamonix%2C%20France.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ed8b9211def8ed8377a31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKuchan%20poses%20in%20the%20French%20ski%20town%20of%20Chamonix.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Callie%20Kuchan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20to%20have%20a%20community%20of%20people%20in%20their%20early%20thirties%2C%20no%20kids%20yet%2C%20it's%20very%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20And%20if%20there%20are%20people%20there%2C%20they%20usually%20end%20up%20moving%20down%20to%20Denver%20or%20moving%20back%20to%20their%20hometown.%20It%20was%20definitely%20challenging%20to%20find%20friends%20because%20you're%20constantly%20starting%20over%20when%20someone%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20definitely%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20come%20right%20out%20of%20college%2C%20or%20when%20they're%20a%20little%20bit%20younger%2C%20to%20work%20the%20seasonal%20jobs%20and%20do%20that%20ski-bum%20lifestyle%20where%20they%20just%20work%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20have%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20really%20missed%20having%20a%20community%20and%20having%20friends%20and%20that%20sort%20of%20situation.%20So%20we%20just%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20this%20isn't%20a%20good%20place%20to%20do%20those%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-colorado-moving-to-midwest-affordable-housing-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697621401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ed7c6be9edfa8eda30b9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-colorado-moving-to-midwest-affordable-housing-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Callie%20Kuchan%20thought%20she'd%20live%20in%20Breckenridge%2C%20Colorado%2C%20forever.%20But%20then%20reality%20set%20in%3A%20She%20couldn't%20afford%20a%20home%20and%20making%20friends%20was%20hard.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-colorado-moving-to-midwest-affordable-housing-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interview%20%7C%20'Rajasthan%20Will%20Re-Elect%20Congress%2C%20Buck%20the%20Trend%20of%20Alternating%20Governments'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18141231%2FThe-Wire-43.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2025.%20Both%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20the%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20not%20announced%20their%20chief%20ministerial%20faces.%20During%20a%20recent%20rally%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20only%20one%20face%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Lotus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20exclusively%20to%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20unit%20chief%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%2C%20about%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20the%20power%20tussle%20between%20his%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20issues%20at%20stake%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20known%20to%20alternate%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20governments%20every%20five%20years.%20However%2C%20Dotasra%20is%20confident%20that%20his%20party%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20will%20buck%20the%20trend%2C%20by%20re-electing%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWill%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20look%20for%20Modi%20%3Cem%3EJi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Nadda%3Cem%3E%20Ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%3F%20We%20are%20here%2C%20available%20for%20the%20people%20and%20we%20will%20be%20here%20even%20after%20elections%20unlike%20Nadda%20and%20Prime%20Minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dotasra%2C%20countering%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20centred%20around%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20its%20national%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWord%20has%20it%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20central%20election%20committee%20has%20already%20cleared%20the%20names%20of%20its%20candidates%20for%20106%20out%20of%20200%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20list%20of%20nominees%20could%20be%20out%20anytime%20soon.%20The%20BJP%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20released%20its%20list%20of%20nominees%20for%2041%20seats%20so%20far%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20discontent%20in%20the%20party.%20Vasundhara%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20camp%20feels%20her%20faction%20in%20the%20party%20has%20been%20sidelined%2C%20with%20the%20party%20ignoring%20the%20names%20proposed%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%20excerpts%20from%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20interview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20a%20criticism%20that%20people%20are%20disappointed%20with%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20to%20Health%20scheme%20because%20private%20hospitals%20are%20not%20being%20able%20to%20manage%20patients.%20People%20now%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20hours%20for%20their%20turn%20in%20private%20hospitals.%20Do%20you%20feel%20that%20your%20government%20has%20been%20too%20hasty%20in%20implementing%20the%20scheme%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20this%20initiative%2C%20which%20we%20have%20taken%20in%20the%20state%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20undertaken%20by%20any%20other%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20people%20are%20getting%20free%20healthcare.%20Also%2C%20if%20you%20see%20in%20Chiranjivi%20Yojna%2C%20people%20are%20getting%20health%20insurance%20as%20well.%20I%20believe%20we%20are%20doing%20better%20compared%20to%20any%20other%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20spoke%20about%20the%20healthcare%20system%2C%20comparing%20it%20to%20other%20states.%20There%20is%20one%20more%20thing%20that%20is%20being%20compared%20to%20other%20states%2C%20i.e.%2C%20NCRB%20data%2C%20which%20says%20that%20Rajasthan%20has%20recorded%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20rape%20cases.%20What%20do%20you%20have%20to%20say%20about%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20this%20because%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20registering%20an%20FIR%20and%20getting%20convicted.%20In%20our%20state%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20we%20do%20is%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20taking%20action%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FYGH0SN_BOHw%3Fsi%3DyKiDKZLJ3W9CPOkb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%