angements%20for%20her%20to%20travel%20for%20the%20award%20ceremony%2C%20and%20she%20was%20supposed%20to%20leave%20on%20October%2017%20for%20Pune.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20October%2016%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20an%20unknown%20faculty%20member%20who%20said%20the%20award%20had%20been%20cancelled%20and%20so%20she%20should%20no%20longer%20travel%20to%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20was%20in%20place%20and%20for%20a%20week%20they%20kept%20reaching%20out%20for%20travel%20arrangements%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20on%20the%2017th%20of%20October%20and%20on%20the%2016th%20of%20October%20around%202%20o%E2%80%99clock%20in%20the%20afternoon%20I%20received%20a%20call%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20phone%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20introduced%20herself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20faculty%20members%20of%20the%20university.%20She%20mentioned%20that%20they%20are%20canceling%20my%20award%20and%20I%20am%20not%20supposed%20to%20travel%20now.%20When%20I%20asked%20for%20the%20reasons%20she%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20that%20they%20are%20facing%20for%20awarding%20me.%20She%20also%20said%20it%20would%20be%20highly%20risky%20for%20me%20to%20travel%20or%20be%20present%20at%20the%20venue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThinking%20that%20this%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20prank%20call%2C%20Nabi%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20Rajeesh%20Kumar%20who%20is%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Mass%20Communication%20and%20Journalism%20to%20check%20about%20the%20authenticity%2C%20as%20he%20had%20been%20her%20single%20point%20of%20contact%20till%20then.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20was%20clueless%20and%20requested%20to%20be%20given%20some%20time%20to%20cross-check%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20called%20me%20back%20sometime%20and%20confirmed%20that%20they%20were%20actually%20canceling%20my%20award%20and%20he%20was%20sorry.%20I%20requested%20they%20put%20all%20of%20this%20over%20email%20and%20give%20me%20the%20reasons%20as%20to%20why%20are%20they%20doing%20so.%20After%20this%20Dhiraj%20Singh%20called%20me%20who%20mentioned%20the%20same%20thing%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20to%20put%20anything%20over%20email.%20They%20were%20just%20calling%20me%20and%20giving%20me%20the%20reason%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20on%20the%20university%20not%20to%20felicitate%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20jury%2C%20who%20too%20had%20not%20been%20told%20about%20the%20cancellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20learning%20about%20the%20cancellation%20of%20Nabi%E2%80%99s%20award%2C%20which%20was%20publicly%20announced%20by%20the%20institute%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20last%20Saturday%2C%20the%20jury%20members%20refused%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20where%20they%20were%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20discussion%20on%20%E2%80%9Cmedia%20and%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJury%20members%20say%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cshocked%E2%80%9D%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20award%20being%20cancelled.%20%E2%80%9CThree%20jury%20members%20were%20in%20Pune%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20and%20participate%20in%20a%20discussion%20(Sunanda%2C%20Sandeep%20and%20I).%20On%20learning%20of%20the%20cancellation%2C%20we%20discussed%20amongst%20ourselves%20and%20decided%20that%20the%20best%20statement%20to%20make%20would%20be%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venu%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKashmiri%20journalists%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20altogether%20different%20level%20of%20censorship%20and%20harassment%20which%20is%20totally%20unconscionable.%20That%20too%20led%20to%20my%20decision%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20director%2C%20Department%20of%20M