7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pulwama%20Attack%3A%20Kin%20of%20Slain%20Jawans%20Demand%20Answers%20from%20Centre%2C%20to%20Hold%20Protest%20March%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123003%2Ffeb0974ca9f958fb65c49849897887b5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20family%20members%20of%2040%20CRPF%20jawans%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%202019%20Pulwama%20attack%20are%20planning%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20march%20in%20Delhi%20on%20November%2026%20to%20demand%20a%20White%20Paper%20from%20the%20government%20to%20fix%20accountability%20for%20the%20alleged%20lapses%20that%20led%20to%20the%20fatal%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20banner%20of%C2%A0Confederation%20of%20Ex-Paramilitary%20Forces%20Welfare%20Associations%2C%20the%20widows%20of%20the%20slain%20jawans%20and%20their%20family%20members%20will%20voice%20their%20demands%20to%20the%20government%20in%20a%20protest%20demonstration%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2026%2C%20which%20is%20celebrated%20as%20Constitution%20Day%2C%20Ranbir%20Singh%2C%20the%20national%20coordinator%20of%20the%20association%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Farmy-welfare-group-to-stage-protest-against-narendra-modi-government-to-demand-answers-on-pulwama-attack%2Fcid%2F1974039%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20plan%20to%20bring%20widows%20and%20family%20members%20of%20the%2040%20CRPF%20jawans%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20terror%20attack.%20It%20has%20been%20over%20four%20years%20since%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20and%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20fix%20accountability%20and%20responsibility%20on%20those%20officials%20whose%20failure%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20our%2040%20jawans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20always%20uses%20the%20nationalism%20plank%20during%20elections%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20come%20clean%20on%20what%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20the%2040%20CRPF%20personnel.%20On%20February%2014%2C%202019%2C%20the%20Jawans%20were%20killed%20when%20a%20bomb%20blew%20up%20the%20bus%20they%20were%20travelling%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20families%20of%20the%2040%20slain%20CRPF%20jawans%20have%20every%20right%20to%20know%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20negligence%20of%20intelligence%20reports%20that%20proved%20fatal%20for%20our%20jawans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20affirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20explosive%20allegations%20made%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20governor%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db8wmHUhLvOI%26t%3D2915s%5C%22%3Einterview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20a%20result%20of%20intelligence%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20In%20that%20interview%2C%20Malik%20said%20that%20Modi%20had%20told%20him%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3Etum%20abhi%20chup%20raho%3C%2Fi%3E%20(you%20keep%20quiet%20now)%E2%80%9D%20after%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20give%20an%20aircraft%20to%20ferry%20jawans%20led%20to%20their%20killing.%20Malik%20also%20went%20on%20to%20repeat%20the%20allegations%20later%20in%20different%20meetings%20that%20he%20attended.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20issued%20summons%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20health%20insurance%20scam%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20over%20four%20years%20since%20then%2C%20but%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20fix%20accountability.%20Winning%20elections%20is%20his%20only%20priority.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20cou