https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkriti-sanon-bonds-with-alia-bhatt-pankaj-tripathi-at-the-national-awards-drops-unseen-pics%2Farticleshow%2F104519262.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Government%20to%20Prohibit%20Sugar%20Exports%20Again%20This%20Season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20prohibit%20sugar%20exports%20this%20season%20(October%202023%20to%20September%202024)%20after%20a%20drop%20in%20production%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20their%20top%20priorities%20are%20to%20produce%20ethanol%20and%20to%20have%20an%20adequate%20supply%20available%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%2C%20especially%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Fgovt-to-prohibit-sugar-export-to-protect-domestic-market%2Farticle67429716.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20Hindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notification%20issued%20on%20October%2028%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20said%20it%20would%20be%20mandatory%20for%20exporters%20to%20have%20a%20prior%20permit%20from%20the%20food%20ministry.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20restriction%20on%20sugar%20exports%20would%20be%20in%20place%20until%20further%20orders%20or%20October%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Director%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20will%20notify%20the%20sugar%20export%20policy%20this%20week%20as%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20previous%20notification%20expires%20on%20October%2031%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20source%20said.%20While%20there%20will%20be%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20earlier%20policy%2C%20there%20are%20two%20likely%20changes%20this%20time%20%E2%80%93%20there%20will%20be%20no%20deadline%2C%20and%20organic%20export%20will%20not%20be%20exempted%20from%20restriction%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20restriction%20will%20halt%20shipments%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findia-set-ban-sugar-exports-first-time-7-years-2023-08-23%2F%5C%22%3Efirst%20time%20in%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20restricted%20the%20amount%20of%20exports%20during%202022-23%20as%20well%2C%20allowing%20mills%20to%20export%20only%206.1%20million%20tonnes%20of%20sugar%20after%20letting%20them%20sell%20a%20record%2011.1%20million%20tonnes%20the%20season%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20in%20August%2C%20a%20government%20source%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20in%20line%20with%20official%20rules%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20primary%20focus%20is%20to%20fulfill%20local%20sugar%20requirements%20and%20produce%20ethanol%20from%20surplus%20sugarcane.%20For%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%20we%20will%20not%20have%20enough%20sugar%20to%20allocate%20for%20export%20quotas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20it%20is%20not%20a%20ban%2C%20it%20has%20the%20same%20meaning%20if%20permits%20are%20not%20issued%20for%20export.%20However%2C%20an%20early%20announcement%20will%20help%20mills%20plan%20how%20much%20sugarcane%20to%20be%20diverted%20to%20make%20sugar%20and%20how%20much%20for%20ethanol%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Fgovt-to-prohibit-sugar-export-to-protect-domestic-market%2Farticle67429716.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20industry%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697613610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Funi