distributors-are-confident-thalapathy-vijays-leo-bloody-sweet-will-earn-big-numbers-despite-not-releasing-in-major-multiplexes-in-the-north-market-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F104518597.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SEBI%20Approached%20OCCRP%20for%20Documents%20on%20Adani%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18121655%2FSEBI_Bhavan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20asked%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20to%20give%20it%20access%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20documents%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20allegations%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20accounting%20fraud%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-sebi-asks-occrp-for-documents%2Farticleshow%2F104510536.cms%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20network%20of%20investigative%20reporters%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%2C%20Rockefeller%20Brothers%20Fund%2C%20Ford%20Foundation%20and%20George%20Soros%20%E2%80%93%20has%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20the%20Indian%20market%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20sources%20of%20information%20are%20accessible%20through%20official%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20cited%20these%20documents%20in%20a%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%20this%20year%20that%20the%20Indian%20conglomerate%20routed%20funds%20to%20two%20foreign%20individuals%20to%20invest%20in%20its%20own%20shares%20using%20Mauritius-based%20platforms.%20The%20report%20provides%20more%20details%20of%20manipulation%20alleged%20by%20the%20US%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20which%20SEBI%20is%20probing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20OCCRP%20told%20SEBI%20that%20its%20long-standing%20policy%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20any%20documents%20beyond%20what%20is%20published.%20The%20Indian%20regulator%20was%20told%20that%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20access%20to%20some%20of%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20September%201%2C%20Bhushan%20tweeted%20one%20of%20the%20key%20documents%20we%20had%20relied%20upon%20that%20showed%20Sebi%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20DRI%20(Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence)%20in%202014%20about%20alleged%20stock%20manipulation.%20On%20September%2018%2C%20a%20filing%20was%20done%20in%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20where%20some%20of%20the%20other%20documents%20were%20attached.%20Clearly%2C%20Bhushan%20has%20access%20to%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20same%20documents%20we%20used%20in%20our%20story.%20Hence%20our%20referral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20January%202014%20DRI%20alert%20was%20sent%20to%20former%20SEBI%20chairman%20U.K.%20Sinha%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20was%20allegedly%20siphoning%20money%20by%20overvaluing%20power%20equipment%20imports%20and%20investing%20them%20in%20listed%20companies%20via%20entities%20located%20in%20Mauritius%20and%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ongoing%20investigation%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%20is%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20two-year-long%20investigation%20by%20a%20network%20of%20reporters%2C%20across%20many%20geographies.%20Information%20was%20sourced%20from%20many%20places%2C%20including%20multiple%20tax%20havens%2C%20bank%20records%20and%20internal%20Adani%20emails.%20All%20of%20our%20sources%20of%20information%20are%20accessible%20to%20Sebi%20through%20official%20channels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20regulator%20has%20told%20the%20top%20court%20that%20shareholders%20linked%20to%20certain%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20in%20Adani%20companies%20are%20located%20in%20tax%20havens%20and%20%E2%80%9Cestablishing%20their%20economic%20interest%20remains%20a%20challenge%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7aadb3d7-4a03-44ba-a01e-8ddd8bce29ed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20report%20which%20alleged%20that%20Adani%20overpriced%20coal%20imports%2C%20which%20saw%20it%20rake%20in%20high%20profits%20but%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20overcharging%20customers.%60%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20it%20by%20Hindenburg%2C%20OCCRP%20and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697611847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18121655%2FSEBI_Bhavan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-occrp-documents-adani-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20network%20of%20investigative%20reporters%20refused%20the%20Indian%20market%20regulator's%20request%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20sources%20of%20information%20are%20accessible%20through%20official%20channels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-occrp-documents-adani-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Song%20Joong%20Ki%20talks%20about%20his%20baby's%20traits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697611534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104518425%2Cimgsize-922002.cms%22%2C%22originI