0would%20encourage%20her%20to%20try%20new%20things%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20worst%20that%20could%20happen%3F%20You%20would%20fail.%20That%20too%20is%20a%20learning%20experience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20artistic%20journey%20with%20mosaics%20began%20when%20she%20was%20in%20her%20thirties.%20One%20day%2C%20when%20she%20was%20beautifying%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20garden%2C%20an%20old%20bench%20became%20her%20first%20artistic%20project%20in%20mosaics.%20With%20her%20father%20being%20a%20property%20developer%2C%20he%20was%20also%20her%20go-to%20person%20for%20chemicals%2C%20gums%20and%20other%20products%20she%20needed%20for%20her%20work.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArt%20can%20be%20inborn%20or%20cultivated.%20My%20art%20was%20mostly%20cultivated%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%20She%20learnt%20mosaic%20art%20from%20books%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20by%20talking%20to%20professional%20tilers%2C%20masons%2C%20hardware%20experts%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20through%20a%20process%20of%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20she%20narrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20style%20of%20mosaic%20work%2C%20she%20collects%20broken%20tiles%20and%20breaks%20them%20further%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273507%2Fkashmir-snow-artists-sculpt-snowman-sculptures-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20see%20what%20pieces%20emerge%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20then%20gets%20creative%20with%20it.%20She%20does%20not%20use%20pre-cut%20mosaics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20459px)%20100vw%2C%20459px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMosaic-bird-bath_11zon-1697535485.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mosaic%20bird%20bath.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMosaic-bird-bath_11zon-1697535485.jpg%2