3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20than%20being%20nutritious%2C%20spent%20grain%20has%20a%20unique%20malty%20flavour%20and%20aroma%2C%20a%20denser%20texture%20to%20the%20bread%2C%20quite%20similar%20to%20Northern%20European%20breads%20like%20rye.%20Lately%2C%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20fans%20who%20wait%20for%20this%20bread%20to%20be%20put%20on%20the%20menu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20says%20that%20she%20was%20able%20to%20upcycle%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20spent%20grain%20last%20financial%20year%20(2022-23)%20and%20saved%20it%20from%20being%20discarded%20as%20trash%20into%20useful%20and%20flavoursome%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20it%20is%20a%20new%20ingredient%2C%20making%20new%20recipes%20from%20it%20was%20a%20little%20challenging.%20Most%20of%20our%20time%20goes%20into%20research%20and%20development.%20I%20have%20even%20written%20a%20handbook%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20spent%20grain%20to%20make%20new%20recipes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20not%20many%20people%20know%20about%20it%20as%20it%20is%20new%20for%20most%20of%20the%20people%20in%20India.%20Our%20main%20purpose%20is%20to%20build%20a%20conversation%20on%20upcycling%20food.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20can%20implement%20my%20ideas%20and%20complete%20the%20circular%20loop%2C%20just%20like%20the%20brewers%20and%20bakers%20from%20the%20past%20did%20it%2C%20the%20old-fashioned%20way!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Elizabeth%20Yorke.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697466790000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20chef%20turned%20food%20researcher%2C%20Elizabeth%20Yorke%20upcycles%20%E2%80%98spent%20grain%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20byproduct%20in%20the%20beer%20brewing%20process%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20breweries%20into%20sustainable%20goodies.%20Last%20year%2C%20she%20saved%201%2C200%20kgs%20of%20spent%20grain%20from%20being%20discarded%20as%20trash%20into%20useful%20and%20flavoursome%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332299%2Fbengaluru-chef-elizabeth-yorke-upcycles-brewery-byproducts-into-sustainable-food-items%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Kumartuli%E2%80%99s%20Icon%20Who%20Broke%20The%20Mold%20%26amp%3B%20Became%20The%201st%20Woman%20Sculptor%20of%20Durga%20Puja%20Idols%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20a%20natural%20flair%20for%20making%20idols%2C%20Mala%20Pal%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20workshop%20only%20because%20she%20was%20a%20woman.%20Wanting%20to%20explore%20her%20talents%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20join%20her%20brother%20in%20idol-making%20when%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324344%2Fportia-putatunda-planet-spiti-foundation-boarding-school-for-underprivileged-kids-help%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efather%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20by%20sheer%20chance%20that%20I%20got%20to%20complete%20an%20idol%20and%20deliver%20it%20to%20the%20client%20one%20day.%20My%20brother%2C%20who%20was%20to%20work%20on%20it%2C%20got%20caught%20up%20elsewhere%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%20With%20a%20deadline%20looming%20large%2C%20I%20took%20on%20the%20work%20as%20a%20challenge%20and%20completed%20it.%20Everyone%20was%20happy%20with%20the%20outcome%20and%20that%20was%20when%20I%20started%20getting%20noticed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297296%2Faward-winning-kumartuli-artisan-mala-pal-trains