%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317884%2Fhow-to-apply-for-drdo-online-certificaton-course-on-ai-cyber-security%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDRDO%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20inviting%20applications%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Junior%20Research%20Fellow%20(JRF)%20and%20Research%20Associate%20(RA)%20in%20Pune%20and%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2012%20open%20positions%20for%20JRF%20and%20one%20opening%20for%20an%20RA%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20in%20Pune%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20seven%20openings%20for%20JRF%20in%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%20Applicants%20must%20not%20be%20more%20than%2028%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2.%20The%20appointment%20of%20applicants%20is%20for%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years%20and%20may%20be%20extendable%20as%20per%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3.%20For%20the%20position%20of%20JRF%2C%20candidates%20must%20have%20a%20BE%2C%20BTech%20in%20electronics%2F%20electronics%20and%20communication%2F%20applied%20electronics%2F%20signal%20processing%2F%20microwave%2F%20microelectronics%2F%20microwave%20engineering%2F%20power%20electronics%2F%20electronics%20and%20instrumentation%2F%20instrumentation%20and%20controls%20and%20similar%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20Candidates%20should%20have%20secured%20a%20first%20division%20with%20NET%2FGATE%20qualification.%20Alternatively%2C%20candidates%20can%20have%20an%20MSc%2C%20ME%20or%20MTech%20in%20the%20above-mentioned%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20Candidates%20can%20also%20possess%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20or%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20di