A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-book-club-read-silence-8676032%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20around%20an%20hour%2C%20the%20attendees%20read%20their%20books%20silently.%20Once%20the%20hour%20is%20over%2C%20the%20participants%20have%20three%20options%3A%20chat%20among%20themselves%2C%20continue%20reading%2C%20or%20leave%20without%20further%20obligations.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20club%20was%20started%20by%20Rachna%20Kalra%2C%20a%20communication%20and%20marketing%20professional%2C%20in%20September%202019%20and%20it%20has%20over%20700%20members%20today.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20is%20to%20get%20people%20back%20to%20reading%20and%20build%20a%20community%20that%20enjoys%20being%20together%20to%20read%20and%20talk%20about%20books%20%E2%80%93%20conversation%20is%20optional.%20l%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20creating%20an%20ambience%20that%20encourages%20people%20to%20read%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20in%20an%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoin%20their%20future%20meeting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FSilentBookClubDelhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20IISER%20Literary%20Club%2C%20Kolkata%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20club%20is%20organised%20by%20students%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20follows%20a%20monthly%20book%20selection%20format.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20each%20month%2C%20the%20group%20meets%20to%20discuss%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20selected%20book%20and%20engage%20in%20lively%20discussion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20the%20book%20club%20is%20that%20it%20also%20organises%20various%20interactive%20activities%20such%20as%20quizzes%2C%20panel%20discussions%2C%20debates%2C%20and%20short%20story%20writing%20competitions!%